---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cafe in Centerville, TN | Coffee, Food & Ice Cream | The Local Place"
  description="The Local Place Cafe in Centerville serves specialty coffee, fresh pastries, breakfast, lunch, and homemade ice cream. Order online or stop by‚Äîopen 6am daily."
  keywords="cafe Centerville TN, coffee shop, breakfast, lunch, ice cream, specialty coffee, local cafe"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>The Local Place Cafe</h1>
      <p>Coffee, Food & Homemade Ice Cream in Centerville</p>
      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" class="hero-cta">Order Online</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><span>Cafe</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="category-intro">
      <h2>Cafe in Centerville, TN</h2>
      <p>
        You want coffee that tastes like someone actually cared. Food that fills you up, not just kills time. Ice cream that melts on your tongue. We open at 6am because we know you need caffeine before the world does. We're here six days a week, turning basic breakfast and lunch into something worth thinking about.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="services-section">
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        {cafeServices.map((service) => (
          <ServiceCard {...service} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-cafe">
      <h2>Why Choose The Local Place Cafe</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>‚òï Specialty Coffee</h3>
          <p>Every espresso shot pulled with care. No burnt coffee, no shortcuts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>ü•ê House-Made Pastries</h3>
          <p>Fresh daily. You can taste the difference between real and store-bought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>üç¶ Homemade Ice Cream</h3>
          <p>Creamy, rich, rotating flavors. This isn't soft-serve. This is real ice cream.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>ü•™ Fresh Lunch</h3>
          <p>Made to order. Paninis grilled hot, salads fresh, nothing sitting around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>üì± Order Online</h3>
          <p>Ready when you arrive. Use Clover to skip the line.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>ü§ù Community Hub</h3>
          <p>Comfortable seating, Wi-Fi, locals who know your order. Come for coffee, stay for the vibe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="featured-items">
      <h2>Customer Favorites</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        {featuredItems.map((item) => (
          <ServiceCard {...item} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cafe-info">
      <h2>Hours & Location</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Hours</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 6 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Saturday:</strong> 9 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>
            111 South Public Square<br />
            Centerville, TN 37033<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-3481">(931) 729-3481</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Order Online</h3>
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Order on Clover ‚Üí</a><br />
            Skip the line. Pick up fresh.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>What Locals Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"I come here every morning for my latte. The barista knows my order, and the pastries are actually fresh. This is my favorite place in Centerville."</p>
          <p><strong>- Michael (Regular)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"The homemade ice cream is insane. I've tried the vanilla bean, chocolate, and salted caramel‚Äîall are better than anything you'd buy at a chain."</p>
